However, the `Add` method expects the first argument to be the namespace URI of the schema, not `null`. 

Here's the corrected code:

```csharp
private XmlSchemaSet GetSchemaSet()
{
    var set = new XmlSchemaSet
    {
        XmlResolver = new XmlUrlResolver()
    };

    var settings = new XmlReaderSettings { DtdProcessing = DtdProcessing.Ignore };

    var reader = XmlReader.Create(
        Path.GetFullPath("SampleXsd/PingContracts.xsd"), settings);

    set.Add("http://schemas.example.com/PingContracts", reader);

    return set;
}
```

